---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="clinconvert — XLS / CSV / JSON → FHIR R4">
  <section class="hero container">
    <h1>把病歷資料轉成 <span class="hl">FHIR R4</span> 標準</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      支援 XLS / XLSX / CSV / JSON 輸入，輸出符合 HL7 FHIR R4 規範的 Bundle JSON、NDJSON、Transaction Bundle。
      適合中小型診所從 Excel 過渡到 FHIR 互通，或開發者測試 FHIR pipeline。
    </p>
    <p class="privacy">
      🔒 <strong>檔案完全在你的瀏覽器處理</strong>。不送到任何伺服器、不上傳、不留紀錄。
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="container converter-section">
    <div class="converter" id="converter">
      <!-- Step 1: Upload -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="step-label">Step 1 · 上傳檔案</div>
        <label for="file-input" class="dropzone" id="dropzone">
          <input type="file" id="file-input" accept=".xlsx,.xls,.csv,.json" hidden />
          <div class="dropzone-content">
            <strong>選擇檔案</strong>，或拖拉檔案到這裡
            <p class="muted">支援 .xlsx · .xls · .csv · .json</p>
          </div>
        </label>
        <div id="file-info" class="file-info" hidden></div>
        <div class="samples muted">
          沒有手邊資料？試試範例：
          <a href="/sample-data/sample-patients.csv" download>sample-patients.csv</a> ·
          <a href="/sample-data/sample-kdigo-observations.csv" download>sample-kdigo-observations.csv</a> ·
          <a href="/sample-data/sample-exclincalc.json" download>sample-exclincalc.json</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2: Datasets + Template -->
      <div class="card" id="step-mapping" hidden>
        <div class="step-label">Step 2 · 選擇映射範本</div>
        <div id="datasets-list"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3: Output -->
      <div class="card" id="step-output" hidden>
        <div class="step-label">Step 3 · 產出 FHIR Bundle</div>
        <div class="output-summary" id="output-summary"></div>
        <div class="output-actions">
          <button type="button" data-format="collection">下載 FHIR Bundle (collection)</button>
          <button type="button" data-format="transaction">下載 Transaction Bundle</button>
          <button type="button" data-format="ndjson">下載 NDJSON</button>
        </div>
        <details class="preview">
          <summary>預覽 JSON</summary>
          <pre id="output-preview"></pre>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="how" class="container">
    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <ol class="steps">
      <li>
        <strong>上傳檔案</strong>
        <p>XLS / XLSX / CSV / JSON。每個 sheet / array 會被視為一個 dataset。</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>選擇映射範本（或自訂）</strong>
        <p>本工具預設四個範本：ExClinCalc Patient / Encounter、健保處方箋、KDIGO 體檢。也可手動指定每個欄位對應到哪個 FHIR field。</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>產出 FHIR Bundle</strong>
        <p>下載成 Bundle JSON（collection）、Transaction Bundle（可 POST 到 FHIR server）、或 NDJSON（批次匯入）。</p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section id="templates" class="container">
    <h2>支援的 FHIR Resource (v1)</h2>
    <ul class="resources">
      <li>
        <code>Patient</code> — 身分、姓名、性別、生日、聯絡方式
        <span class="muted">·  <a href="https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/patient.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HL7 spec</a></span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <code>Encounter</code> — 就診紀錄、狀態、時間段
        <span class="muted">·  <a href="https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/encounter.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HL7 spec</a></span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <code>Observation</code> — 檢驗值、生命徵象（含 LOINC 編碼）
        <span class="muted">·  <a href="https://hl7.org/fhir/R4/observation.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HL7 spec</a></span>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3>規劃中（v2）</h3>
    <ul class="resources muted">
      <li><code>Medication</code> / <code>Condition</code> / <code>Procedure</code></li>
      <li>HL7 v2 message → FHIR R4</li>
      <li>反向轉換：FHIR → XLS（給診所人員看的格式）</li>
      <li>對接 HAPI FHIR public test server 做 round-trip 驗證</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="container context-section">
    <div class="context">
      <h2>關於這個工具</h2>
      <p>
        衛福部 2026 年目標完成全台<strong>醫學中心 FHIR 電子病歷互通</strong>（已有中山、長庚、馬偕三家示範醫院）。
        到 2028 年將擴及衛生所與診所。
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>clinconvert 是給「中小型診所、護理之家、研究者」過渡到 FHIR 用的轉換工具</strong>。
        大醫院的 HIS DB → FHIR 通常用 MIRTH Connect 或 HAPI FHIR 等 ETL 框架，這套工具填補的是「資料還在 Excel 階段」的場景。
      </p>
      <p>設計選擇：</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>瀏覽器本地處理</strong> ── 醫療資料不離開使用者裝置，符合個資法精神</li>
        <li><strong>Adapter pattern</strong> ── 容易擴充支援新的輸入 / 輸出格式</li>
        <li><strong>開源</strong> ── 完整程式碼在 GitHub，歡迎 fork 客製成自家工具</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .hero { padding: 4rem 20px 2rem; max-width: 760px; }
    .hero h1 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hl { color: var(--c-primary); }
    .lead { font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--c-text); }
    .privacy { font-size: 0.95rem; padding: 0.85rem 1rem; background: #ecfdf5; border-left: 3px solid var(--c-success); border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0; color: var(--c-success); }
    section { padding: 2rem 20px; }

    .converter-section { padding-top: 1rem; }
    .converter { display: grid; gap: 1.25rem; }
    .card { padding: 1.5rem; background: var(--c-bg-soft); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--c-border); }
    .step-label { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--c-primary); letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.85rem; }

    .dropzone { display: block; padding: 2.5rem 1rem; border: 2px dashed var(--c-border); border-radius: 10px; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s; background: white; }
    .dropzone:hover, .dropzone.drag-over { border-color: var(--c-primary); background: #f0fdfa; }
    .dropzone strong { color: var(--c-primary); }
    .dropzone p { margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; }

    .file-info { margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0.85rem 1rem; background: white; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid var(--c-border); font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .file-info strong { color: var(--c-text); }
    .samples { margin-top: 0.85rem; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    .samples a { color: var(--c-primary); }

    .dataset { padding: 1rem; background: white; border: 1px solid var(--c-border); border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 0.85rem; }
    .dataset-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .dataset-name { font-weight: 600; }
    .dataset-meta { color: var(--c-text-soft); font-size: 0.85rem; }
    .dataset select { padding: 0.4rem 0.6rem; border: 1px solid var(--c-border); border-radius: 6px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .dataset-preview { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--c-text-muted); margin-top: 0.5rem; }

    .output-summary { margin-bottom: 1rem; padding: 0.85rem 1rem; background: white; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid var(--c-border); font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .output-actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
    .output-actions button { padding: 0.65rem 1rem; background: var(--c-primary); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 6px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.15s; }
    .output-actions button:hover { background: var(--c-primary-light); }
    .preview { margin-top: 1rem; }
    .preview summary { cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--c-text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .preview pre { max-height: 320px; overflow: auto; font-size: 0.78rem; line-height: 1.5; }

    .steps { list-style: none; counter-reset: step; display: grid; gap: 1.25rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .steps li { padding-left: 3rem; position: relative; }
    .steps li::before {
      counter-increment: step;
      content: counter(step);
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      width: 2rem;
      height: 2rem;
      background: var(--c-primary);
      color: white;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .resources { list-style: none; display: grid; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .resources li { padding: 0.6rem 0.85rem; background: var(--c-bg-soft); border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid var(--c-border); }
    .context { background: var(--c-bg-soft); border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; }
    .context ul { padding-left: 1.25em; }
    .context li { color: var(--c-text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.4em; }

    .error { color: var(--c-error); padding: 0.6rem 0.85rem; background: #fef2f2; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid #fecaca; margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  </style>

  <script>
    import { parseXlsx } from '../lib/adapters/xlsx';
    import { parseJson } from '../lib/adapters/json';
    import { ALL_TEMPLATES, suggestTemplate, type MappingTemplate } from '../lib/mapping/templates';
    import { buildResource } from '../lib/fhir/builders';
    import {
      toCollectionBundle,
      toTransactionBundle,
      toNdjson,
      toPrettyJson,
      triggerDownload,
    } from '../lib/output/bundle';
    import type { NormalizedDataset } from '../lib/core/internal-model';
    import type { FhirAnyResource } from '../lib/fhir/types';

    // === State ===
    interface DatasetState {
      dataset: NormalizedDataset;
      templateId: string | 'skip';
    }
    let datasetStates: DatasetState[] = [];

    // === DOM refs ===
    const $file = document.getElementById('file-input') as HTMLInputElement;
    const $dropzone = document.getElementById('dropzone') as HTMLLabelElement;
    const $fileInfo = document.getElementById('file-info') as HTMLDivElement;
    const $stepMapping = document.getElementById('step-mapping') as HTMLDivElement;
    const $datasetsList = document.getElementById('datasets-list') as HTMLDivElement;
    const $stepOutput = document.getElementById('step-output') as HTMLDivElement;
    const $outputSummary = document.getElementById('output-summary') as HTMLDivElement;
    const $outputPreview = document.getElementById('output-preview') as HTMLPreElement;

    // === Drag & drop ===
    $dropzone.addEventListener('dragover', (e) => {
      e.preventDefault();
      $dropzone.classList.add('drag-over');
    });
    $dropzone.addEventListener('dragleave', () => $dropzone.classList.remove('drag-over'));
    $dropzone.addEventListener('drop', (e: DragEvent) => {
      e.preventDefault();
      $dropzone.classList.remove('drag-over');
      const file = e.dataTransfer?.files[0];
      if (file) handleFile(file);
    });

    $file.addEventListener('change', () => {
      const file = $file.files?.[0];
      if (file) handleFile(file);
    });

    async function handleFile(file: File) {
      $fileInfo.hidden = false;
      $fileInfo.innerHTML = `<strong>${file.name}</strong> · ${(file.size / 1024).toFixed(1)} KB · 解析中...`;

      try {
        let datasets: NormalizedDataset[];
        const ext = file.name.toLowerCase().split('.').pop();
        if (ext === 'json') {
          const text = await file.text();
          datasets = await parseJson(text, { sourceName: file.name });
        } else {
          datasets = await parseXlsx(file);
        }

        if (datasets.length === 0) {
          $fileInfo.innerHTML = `<span class="error">無法解析資料（無有效列）</span>`;
          return;
        }

        $fileInfo.innerHTML = `<strong>${file.name}</strong> · 找到 ${datasets.length} 個 dataset、共 ${datasets.reduce((s, d) => s + d.records.length, 0)} 筆`;
        showMapping(datasets);
      } catch (err) {
        const msg = err instanceof Error ? err.message : String(err);
        $fileInfo.innerHTML = `<span class="error">解析失敗：${msg}</span>`;
      }
    }

    function showMapping(datasets: NormalizedDataset[]) {
      datasetStates = datasets.map((ds) => {
        const suggested = suggestTemplate(ds.sourceDescription);
        return {
          dataset: ds,
          templateId: suggested?.id ?? 'skip',
        };
      });

      $datasetsList.innerHTML = datasetStates
        .map((s, i) => renderDataset(s, i))
        .join('');

      // Bind change events
      $datasetsList.querySelectorAll<HTMLSelectElement>('select[data-idx]').forEach((sel) => {
        sel.addEventListener('change', (e) => {
          const idx = parseInt(sel.dataset.idx ?? '0', 10);
          datasetStates[idx].templateId = (e.target as HTMLSelectElement).value;
          updateOutput();
        });
      });

      $stepMapping.hidden = false;
      updateOutput();
    }

    function renderDataset(state: DatasetState, idx: number): string {
      const { dataset, templateId } = state;
      const sample = dataset.records[0]?.fields ?? {};
      const sampleStr = Object.entries(sample)
        .slice(0, 4)
        .map(([k, v]) => `${k}: ${String(v ?? '').slice(0, 30)}`)
        .join(' · ');

      const options = [
        `<option value="skip" ${templateId === 'skip' ? 'selected' : ''}>— 不轉換（跳過）—</option>`,
        ...ALL_TEMPLATES.map(
          (t) =>
            `<option value="${t.id}" ${templateId === t.id ? 'selected' : ''}>${t.resourceType} · ${t.name}</option>`
        ),
      ].join('');

      return `
        <div class="dataset">
          <div class="dataset-header">
            <span class="dataset-name">${escapeHtml(dataset.sourceDescription)}</span>
            <span class="dataset-meta">${dataset.records.length} 筆 · ${dataset.columns.length} 欄</span>
          </div>
          <label>
            <span class="muted">套用範本：</span>
            <select data-idx="${idx}">${options}</select>
          </label>
          <div class="dataset-preview">第一筆預覽：${escapeHtml(sampleStr || '(空)')}</div>
        </div>
      `;
    }

    function escapeHtml(s: string): string {
      return s
        .replace(/&/g, '&amp;')
        .replace(/</g, '&lt;')
        .replace(/>/g, '&gt;')
        .replace(/"/g, '&quot;');
    }

    function getTemplate(id: string): MappingTemplate | undefined {
      return ALL_TEMPLATES.find((t) => t.id === id);
    }

    function generateResources(): FhirAnyResource[] {
      const resources: FhirAnyResource[] = [];
      for (const s of datasetStates) {
        if (s.templateId === 'skip') continue;
        const tpl = getTemplate(s.templateId);
        if (!tpl) continue;
        for (const record of s.dataset.records) {
          try {
            resources.push(buildResource(record, tpl));
          } catch (err) {
            console.error('build error', record.sourceRef, err);
          }
        }
      }
      return resources;
    }

    function updateOutput() {
      const resources = generateResources();
      if (resources.length === 0) {
        $stepOutput.hidden = true;
        return;
      }
      $stepOutput.hidden = false;
      const byType = resources.reduce<Record<string, number>>((acc, r) => {
        acc[r.resourceType] = (acc[r.resourceType] ?? 0) + 1;
        return acc;
      }, {});
      $outputSummary.innerHTML = `共 <strong>${resources.length}</strong> 個 resource：${Object.entries(byType)
        .map(([k, v]) => `${k} × ${v}`)
        .join(' · ')}`;
      const bundle = toCollectionBundle(resources);
      $outputPreview.textContent = toPrettyJson(bundle).slice(0, 4000) + (resources.length > 5 ? '\n... (truncated for preview)' : '');
    }

    // Download handlers
    document.querySelectorAll<HTMLButtonElement>('.output-actions button').forEach((btn) => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const resources = generateResources();
        if (resources.length === 0) return;
        const fmt = btn.dataset.format ?? 'collection';
        const ts = new Date().toISOString().slice(0, 19).replace(/[T:]/g, '-');
        if (fmt === 'collection') {
          triggerDownload(
            toPrettyJson(toCollectionBundle(resources)),
            `fhir-bundle-${ts}.json`,
            'application/fhir+json'
          );
        } else if (fmt === 'transaction') {
          triggerDownload(
            toPrettyJson(toTransactionBundle(resources)),
            `fhir-transaction-${ts}.json`,
            'application/fhir+json'
          );
        } else if (fmt === 'ndjson') {
          triggerDownload(
            toNdjson(resources),
            `fhir-${ts}.ndjson`,
            'application/x-ndjson'
          );
        }
      });
    });
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
